# Allowlist: only sync these remote paths (one per line).
# When this file has any non-comment entries, nextclouddock runs one
# nextcloudcmd invocation per listed path instead of a single full sync.
# Paths are relative to the Nextcloud root (no leading slash required).
# Both top-level folders and nested paths are supported.
# When this file is empty or absent, all remote content is synced (default).
#
# Examples:
#   Documents
#   Photos
#   Documents/Work/Projects
